ADDITIONAL NOTICE — RESEARCH AND EDUCATIONAL USE ONLY

MedVix is an educational tool and research prototype developed for university
coursework. It is NOT a regulated medical device and MUST NOT be used to make
real clinical decisions for individual patients. The synthetic datasets bundled
with the application are generated programmatically and do not represent any
real patient population.

For third-party library, dataset, and asset attribution, see ATTRIBUTION.md
and DATA_LICENSES.md.
